{
  "id": "nce2-l75",
  "title": "Lesson 75: SOS",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/75ÔºçSOS.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How did the woman get help?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.24,
      "endTime": 14.44
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "When a light passenger plane flew off course some time ago,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.45,
      "endTime": 19.67
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "it crashed in the mountains and its pilot was killed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 19.68,
      "endTime": 25.24
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The only passengers, a young woman and her two baby daughters, were unhurt.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.25,
      "endTime": 33.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It was the middle of winter.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.51,
      "endTime": 36.07
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Snow lay thick on the ground.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.08,
      "endTime": 39.76
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The woman knew that the nearest village was miles away.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.77,
      "endTime": 45.04
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When it grew dark, she turned a suitcase into a bed and put the children inside it,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.05,
      "endTime": 53.19
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "covering them with all the clothes she could find.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 53.2,
      "endTime": 57.92
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "During the night, it got terribly cold.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.93,
      "endTime": 62.46
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The woman kept as near as she could to the children and even tried to get into the case herself, but it was too small.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 62.47,
      "endTime": 74.03
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Early next morning,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.04,
      "endTime": 75.78
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "she heard planes passing overhead and wondered how she could send a signal.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.79,
      "endTime": 82.69
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Then she had an idea. She stamped out the letters 'SOS' in the snow.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "endTime": 91.97
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Fortunately, a pilot saw the signal and sent a message by radio to the nearest town.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 91.98,
      "endTime": 100.46
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It was not long before a helicopter arrived on the scene to rescue the survivors of the plane crash.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.47,
      "endTime": 105.47
    }
  ]
}